Privacy Notice of the Slate Science Group
Slate science Pty Ltd., together with its Affiliates (the “
Slate Science Group
”) offer educational technology solutions. Among other activities, we offer a platform that helps to develop mathematical skills through interactive math games of (the “
Platform
”), available through matific.com (the “
Site
”) to empower mathematical education. We also provide various support and service activities related to the Platform (“
Services
”).
Data privacy is important to us. This means that we process data with due care, while adopting and combining industry standard data collection, storage, and processing practices with security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of a user's personal information and always in accordance with applicable data protection laws. We are constantly seeking to improve ourselves in this field, for instance, by performing annual data-privacy and security compliance audits carried out by independent advisors.
SHORT PRIVACY NOTICE FOR STUDENTS
Hi! Welcome to our site! Before you get to solving problems, winning games, getting points and collecting monsters, here are some ground rules:
We collect information about you. We collect your name and data about what you do within the Matific platform. this data isn’t shared with anyone outside of Matific and never will be.
Log in to the Site with a login name that you got from your parent or your teacher. Please do not try to register on your own.
We want you to concentrate while playing our games, that's why there is no way on our Site to get in touch with your classmates or other friends.
We believe in hard work, so, on our Site there are no shortcuts. You will be able to gain points only by playing by yourselves since our Site does not allow to purchase points for real money or similar means in order to advance.
