General
Please see below some features that the Site and the Platform do NOT support:
Social or any interactions between different users. In fact, within the Platform, users  are not visible one to another;
Creation or uploading of any content by users. All the content is created by Slate Science Group, for more information concerning the content the Platform, please see our
Terms of Use
Any kind of additional purchases within a Site by any user;
The Site and the Platform does not display any advertising.
“Do Not Track” Disclosures
Under certain state laws it is required to indicate whether we honor “Do Not Track” settings in your browser concerning targeted advertising. Matific adheres to the standards set out in this Privacy Notice and does not monitor or respond to Do Not Track browser requests or other opt-out mechanisms.
FERPA NOTICE
To the extent we receive  any Personal Data in a capacity of a "School Official" pursuant to a disclosure from an educational agency or institution, Please be advised that (a) the educational agency or institution must execute a separate purchase order and a data processing addendum (DPA) thereto, that restricts the use by us of any such Personal Data to the provision of the Services; and (b)the Personal Data will only be used in accordance with this Privacy Notice and the DPA; and (c) as between us and the educational agency or institution, the control over any such Personal Data is with the educational agency or institution.
